body:

A member in a community always has a role as either reader, curator, manager or owner. See [about communities](../../about-communities/) for details on roles and their permissions.

Only community managers and owners can change roles of other members, and only owners can change roles to an owner.

---
tocdesc: Learn how to change the role of an existing member.
